---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Lion City Locking Library">
  <div class="about-page">
    <section class="page-hero">
      <p class="page-label">About</p>

      <h1>About Lion City Locking Library</h1>

      <p class="page-description">
        An independent archive documenting the history, culture, and community
        memory of Locking dance in Singapore.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="essay-section">
      <h2>Why this archive exists</h2>

      <p>
        Lion City Locking Library was created to preserve the stories, people,
        events, and cultural memory that shaped Singapore's Locking scene.
      </p>

      <p>
        Much of dance history lives through oral memory — conversations,
        workshops, battles, performances, friendships, and community spaces.
        This archive aims to document those histories before they are lost.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="essay-section">
      <h2>What this archive documents</h2>

      <p>
        The archive includes interviews, timelines, contributor profiles,
        educational writing, and community-submitted memories related to Locking
        and Campbellocking in Singapore.
      </p>

      <p>
        It is not intended to be a final or complete version of history.
        Instead, it is a growing record shaped by research, interviews, and
        contributions from the community.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
